messages.content: What does the Cyber Dolphin plugin do for ComfyUI?
Cyber Dolphin is a plugin that allows users to get image prompts from OpenAI or a compatible API. It uses the `gpt-3.5-turbo` model by default.
Which models can the Cyber Dolphin plugin compare when generating images from text?
Cyber Dolphin can compare image results from DALLÂ·E and local stable diffusion models to determine which one generates better images from text prompts.
What is the default model Cyber Dolphin uses to get image prompts?
By default, Cyber Dolphin uses the `gpt-3.5-turbo` model to get image prompts.
Can Cyber Dolphin be used with other API providers besides OpenAI?
Yes, Cyber Dolphin can be used with a compatible API besides OpenAI, as long as it is compatible with the plugin's functionality.
